{"tid":452305,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"goto導演呼籲DC和漫威漫畫的粉絲們停止之間的爭論","createTime":"2017-10-30T05:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T14:16:41.000Z","uid":861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04a8b935dfc70fe3142ad266f2bb37a5e1a98a56","tid":452305,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"最近，《銀河守護隊》系列導演詹姆斯.岡恩 (James Gunn) 通過社群平台 Twitter 呼籲DC和漫威漫畫的粉絲們停止之間的爭論，稱其為一種無止盡且愚蠢的行為。<br />\n<br />\n「1. 每一次我提到DC，無論是什麼，我的推文自動會變成有關於《蝙蝠俠大戰超人》的無止盡互嗆比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n「2. 你們永遠也無法說服對方，這僅僅是在浪費一堆的能量。」<br />\n<br />\n「3. 至少你們在為川普而大喊大叫時，那是國際的大事。」<br />\n<br />\n「4. 但這只是一部兩歲的電影，有些人喜歡，有些人不喜歡。為什麼別人的意見對你那麼重要？」<br />\n<br />\n「5. 作為漫威和DC的死忠粉，你們彼此之間所擁有的共同點，比你們與世上其他人的來得多。」<br />\n<br />\n「6. 所以為什麼花那麼多的時間去討厭彼此？這樣很愚蠢，拜託停下來，不要再這樣做了。」<br />\n<br />\n「7. 但最起碼的是，你們這樣做時，別叫上我。我已經靜音你們當中的許多人了，但不是所有人。感謝。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/132059_6858f1c95c910f0a81113618e3b0d095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F132059_6858f1c95c910f0a81113618e3b0d095.jpg&h=1785cff2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b418d1c98b9ed4d38ad95255a7c1cbcc2a4d8f0e","tid":452305,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/jason-momoa-fuck-marvel-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F03%2Fjason-momoa-fuck-marvel-poster.jpg&h=899d24f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Sp-XMNm12UM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSp-XMNm12UM&d=AGvHFC3Ye9q1nZzXwKH0%2F8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=c8bf8b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Sp-XMNm12UM</a>"},{"pid":"bcca902548b44bce1b5a0f80f3d5b6874eef3b67","tid":452305,"uid":861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"cited